Package: adlyseR
Title: Cross-Channel Ad & Traffic Analysis Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R:
    person("Paul", "Newnes", email = "paul@deducive.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A reusable toolkit for pulling, harmonising, and combining
    ad performance data from Meta, Google Ads, and LinkedIn, together
    with GA4 traffic for a campaign's landing pages. Built from working
    patterns in the NACS Show media-planning project. Each campaign is
    described by a lightweight config object so the same code can serve
    multiple clients and campaigns.
